            <div class="title">
                Army Estimates, 1951–52
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1951-03-08/debates/05d3150b-bdbf-4cfe-897d-e2ef575392f9/TerritorialArmy" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
