        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-a7f3563f-ec31-4dac-ac1c-a4624563cf60">
                Lord John Hope  (Edinburgh, Pentlands)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a7f3563f-ec31-4dac-ac1c-a4624563cf60" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-08/debates/17bc9e58-99b5-4a1c-8924-6fd12fd3525f/ArmyEstimates1951%E2%80%9352#contribution-a7f3563f-ec31-4dac-ac1c-a4624563cf60">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will the right hon. Gentleman pass that on to the Lord President of the Council, who credited this side of the House with the very reverse attitude in his speech only a few days ago?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a7f3563f-ec31-4dac-ac1c-a4624563cf60" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-08/debates/17bc9e58-99b5-4a1c-8924-6fd12fd3525f/ArmyEstimates1951%E2%80%9352#contribution-a7f3563f-ec31-4dac-ac1c-a4624563cf60">
