                Mr. Hamilton
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-39a8edf2-d7a7-42f1-8ba5-854c265eba90" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-03-08/debates/17bc9e58-99b5-4a1c-8924-6fd12fd3525f/ArmyEstimates1951%E2%80%9352#contribution-39a8edf2-d7a7-42f1-8ba5-854c265eba90">
